                            <comment id="15411172" author="shalinmangar" created="Mon, 8 Aug 2016 01:53:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The bug was that BaseCdcrDistributedZkTest#updateMappingsFromZk was called while restarting nodes which used to replace the CloudJettyRunner instances with new ones without closing the resources being used by any existing CloudJettyRunner. The fix is to ensure that any old resources are closed before the CloudJettyRunner instances are replaced.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
